sections.heading: to 61-12-21 - Repealed.
sections.text:
Repeals.— Laws 1997, ch. 89, § 21 repealed 61-12-1 to 61-12-21 NMSA 1978, relating to physical therapy, effective July 1, 1997. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1996 NMSA onNMOneSource.com.For present comparable provisions,see61-12D-1 NMSA 1978 et seq.

Compiler's notes.— Section 61-12-21 NMSA 1978 was amended by Laws 1997, ch. 46, § 12 to extend the sunset dates of Chapter 61, Article 12 NMSA 1978. However, due to the repeal of the article by Laws 1997, ch. 89, § 21, the amendment was not set out.
